      "score": 874,
      "comments": 994,
      "author": "simonw",
      "published": "2026-05-27T16:39:13Z",
      "bullets": [
        "OpenAI and Anthropic secured PMF as developers transitioned from experimental chatbots to integrating APIs directly into core production infrastructure.",
        "Claude 3.5 Sonnet dominates software engineering workflows, while GPT-4o leads in multimodal tasks, driving distinct enterprise use cases for each vendor.",
        "Production value has shifted from raw LLM outputs to reliable RAG architectures, structured JSON outputs, and autonomous agentic tool-use loops."
      ]
    },
