      "bullets": [
        "CLI search and processing utilities like ripgrep, fzf, and jq dramatically accelerate codebase navigation and data manipulation workflows.",
        "Declarative environment managers like Nix and direnv solve reproducible, localized developer environment provisioning and dependency management.",
        "Advanced terminal-based Git tools, including lazygit and git-delta, streamline version control visualization, diffing, and history navigation."
      ]
